OL,3,CClapping for NHS during pandemic may
OL,4,Chave been 'dangerous', says ombudsman
OL,6,FThe Telegraph reported that evidence
OL,7,Fsubmitted to the investigation showed
OL,8,F27,479 complaints about the NHS in
OL,9,FEngland to the ombudsman in 2023/24,
OL,10,Fwith two in three at least partly
OL,11,Fupheld.
OL,13,FCommenting on the rise in complaints
OL,14,Ffrom 18,727 received in 2020/21, Ms
OL,15,FHilsenrath said: "I think it does
OL,16,Fspeak to a change in attitude towards
OL,17,Fthe NHS and a far lower degree of
OL,18,Fhappiness with services.
OL,26,@wD@ROU
