OL,3,CClapping for NHS during pandemic may
OL,4,Chave been 'dangerous', says ombudsman
OL,6,F"Of course, people were enormously
OL,7,Fgrateful for the extraordinary efforts
OL,8,Fthat people in NHS went to during that
OL,9,Ftime, including risking their own
OL,10,Fpersonal safety.
OL,12,F"I also know that the national mood
OL,13,Fhas changed since then, and I think
OL,14,Fit's incredibly difficult as an NHS
OL,15,Fworker to consistently read about the
OL,16,Ffailings in your service, and how
OL,17,Fyou're letting people down."
