OL,3,CClapping for NHS during pandemic may
OL,4,Chave been 'dangerous', says ombudsman
OL,6,FThe health service ombudsman
OL,7,Fcontinued: "There is an argument I
OL,8,Fhave heard that clapping for the NHS
OL,9,Fduring the pandemic was quite a
OL,10,Fdangerous thing to do ... because no
OL,11,Forganisation can be a national
OL,12,Freligion, and no organisation should
OL,13,Fbe beyond constructive criticism.
OL,15,F"I don't think that it is helpful for
OL,16,Fany organisation to be treated as
OL,17,Freligion."
