OL,3,CClapping for NHS during pandemic may
OL,4,Chave been 'dangerous', says ombudsman
OL,6,FMs Hilsenrath said there was "a lack
OL,7,Fof consistency" in the NHS, adding
OL,8,Fthat "the ultimate price for failure
OL,9,Fis tragedy".
OL,11,FShe said: "An NHS that isn't listening
OL,12,Fisn't learning, and that's what takes
OL,13,Fyou into repeat behaviours, and that's
OL,14,Fthe single critical thing that we see.
OL,15,FAnd I'm afraid we see it over and over
OL,16,Fagain.
OL,18,F"When big things go wrong and terrible
OL,19,Fthings happen you get the NHS saying
OL,20,F'never again', but actually it's just
OL,21,Fnot true.
