OL,3,CClapping for NHS during pandemic may
OL,4,Chave been 'dangerous', says ombudsman
OL,6,F"Being patient-centric lies at the
OL,7,Fheart of that, because until the NHS
OL,8,Flistens more with people when things
OL,9,Fgo wrong and before they go wrong, of
OL,10,Fcourse, those mistakes will continue
OL,11,Fto be made."
OL,13,FMs Hilsenrath said the regulatory
OL,14,Flandscape was in "urgent need of
OL,15,Freform", adding there was a "vast
OL,16,Famount of duplication".
