OL,3,CClapping for NHS during pandemic may
OL,4,Chave been 'dangerous', says ombudsman
OL,6,FShe said: "It's very difficult for
OL,7,Fregulators in health to speak with a
OL,8,Fclear and united voice, because
OL,9,Fthere's just so many of them, and they
OL,10,Fall have slightly different but
OL,11,Foverlapping roles.
OL,13,F"The organisations in question, the
OL,14,FNHS, tend to get faced by multiple
OL,15,Frecommendations which all come from
OL,16,Fdifferent people, and ... of course,
OL,17,Fit's a grossly inefficient way to run
OL,18,Fanything."
