OL,3,CClapping for NHS during pandemic may
OL,4,Chave been 'dangerous', says ombudsman
OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "The NHS is broken
OL,8,Fbut we are determined to get it back
OL,9,Fon its feet so it can be there for all
OL,10,Fof us when we need it.
OL,12,F"We will be honest about the
OL,13,Fchallenges facing the health service
OL,14,Fand will work to tackle them.
OL,16,F"The independent investigation into
OL,17,Fthe NHS by Lord Darzi is a step
OL,18,Ftowards identifying and solving these
OL,19,Fproblems as we create an NHS fit for
OL,20,Fthe future."
